The '''Slime Sea''' was a large body of [[Water/Legends|water]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Sullust/Legends|Sullust]]. It received its name from its disgusting nature.

The many sailors that worked the waters gave it a crude name from their vulgar language.

